=head1 NAME

replicator - ZFS continual data replication daemon

=head1 SYNOPSIS

	replicator [-1] [-x] [-C config] [-g groupname] [ -vLEVEL ]

-g: replicate only this group (default all groups)
-1: replicate groups once only, then stop (normally, continue running forever)
-x: do not detach from terminal; log to STDERR (normally, syslog/daemon)
-C: configuration from specified file (default /etc/replicator.conf)

-vN: logging level:
           0 no logging at all
           1 default level
           2 voluminous debugging information

=cut
